milestones.description: de Silva and Ranatunga's 45-run partnership is SL's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 35 between Guy de Alwis and Ratnayake
Madugalle has broken the record for most sixes (6) in ODIs for SL, going past Duleep Mendis's 5
This is the lowest match aggregate (273) involving teams New Zealand & Sri Lanka in ODIs
de Silva has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (26) for SL, going past Duleep Mendis
